			<h2>What is AthleteTrax?</h2>
			<p>AthleteTrax is a Web-based platform for NCAA athletic programs that bridges the gap between an athletic administration and its student athletes through integrated scheduling, instant communication, and data and forms management.</p> 
			<br>
			<h2>What is our Mission?</h2>
			<p>AthleteTrax aims to maximize an NCAA student athlete's academic performance, while simultaneously simplifying the daily lives of collegiate athletic program administrators.</p>
			<br>
			<h2>When was AthleteTrax founded?</h2>
			<p> AthleteTrax LLC was founded in December 2011 in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania by Jon Halpern, Reinaldo Coriano, Betsy Zander, and Brian Jeffrey Gross. </p>
