			<h2>Why are we passionate about NCAA sports?</h2>
			<p> Each of the four AthleteTrax Co-founders have competed at high levels in a wide range of sports, from football and golf to ice hockey and gymnastics. The four co-founders were all recruited to play NCAA athletics in one sport or another, and two of them have had personal experience playing Division I sports. We know what it's like to be an NCAA athlete. We know how hard it is to succeed both on and off the playing field. We want to be the ones who finally make a difference in the futures of NCAA student athletes, because we have all faced the harsh reality of just how hard it is to play professional sports.</p>
			<br>
